    "Agile embraces changes in requirements even late in the development process.",
    "This flexibility allows teams to respond quickly to evolving priorities or new insights.",
    "Agile encourages forming cross-functional, self-organizing teams with all the skills necessary to complete the project within the team, promoting better communication and collaboration.",
    "Regular reviews and feedback sessions are integral to Agile methodologies.",
    "This constant feedback loop helps identify and address issues promptly, ensuring the project remains aligned with stakeholders' expectations."
